data.description: A fabulous 2 story home. This charming home features entry foyer with high ceilings, large light and bright living room with a cozy fireplace, spacious open kitchen with granite countertops, plenty of counter and cabinet space, oak cabinets and a large island. Great floor plan. The main level has the primary bedroom, large walk-in closet, primary bathroom with dual sinks and separate shower. Upstairs features a Gameroom, two bedrooms and one full bathroom. Great location!!! in a quiet secluded neighborhood. House is located on a cul-de-sac at the end of the street. No back neighbors!
